Package: KnnDist
Type: Package
Title: Kernal Nearest Neighbour classification with distance inputs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ardern", "Hulme-Beaman", email = "ardernhb@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Ardern Hulme-Beaman [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Ardern Hulme-Beaman <ardernhb@gmail.com>
Description: This package takes distance inputs constructed by the user and returns classifications using Kernal Nearest Neighbour (K-NN) methods. Current implimentation includes a simple majority vote process or a simple weighting system using the distances supplied as weights.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/ArdernHB/KnnDist
BugReports: https://github.com/ArdernHB/KnnDist
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
